**Sukanya Samriddhi Yojana (SSY)** is a government-backed savings scheme for the girl child, offering the highest interest rate among all small savings schemes — currently 8.2% p.a. (Q1 FY 2026-27). Deposits are made for 15 years; the account matures after 21 years from opening or on the girl's marriage after age 18.
